query:
SELECT i.id, i.productId, i.locationId, i.batch, i.quantity, i.status, wl.code as locationCode 
FROM inventory i 
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id 
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC LIMIT 10
